'''玛格丽特·蔡斯·马德琳·史密斯'''（{{lang-en|'''Margaret Madeline Chase Smith'''}}，{{bd|1897年|12月14日|1995年|5月29日|catIdx=S}}）<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.mcslibrary.org/bio/ |title=SENATOR, REPRESENTATIVE, AMERICAN |accessdate=2016-07-09 |archive-date=2016-06-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160627130212/http://www.mcslibrary.org/bio/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，[[美国|美国]]政治人物、[[美國空軍|美國空軍]][[美國空軍預備役司令部|預備役]][[中校|中校]]<ref name="Famous American Women"/><ref name="The Surprising Mrs. Smith"/><ref name="Military Men Numerous on Capitol Hill"/>。史密斯為[[共和黨_(美國)|共和黨]]黨员，曾任[[美国众议院|美国众议院]]议员（1940年-1949年），后担任[[缅因州|缅因州]][[美国参议院|参议员]]。<ref name=congress>{{cite news|work=Biographical Directory of the United States Congress|title=SMITH, Margaret Chase, (1897 - 1995)|url=http://bioguide.congress.gov/scripts/biodisplay.pl?index=s000590|accessdate=2016-07-09|archive-date=2011-04-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110404063249/http://bioguide.congress.gov/scripts/biodisplay.pl?index=S000590|dead-url=no}}</ref>她是缅因州第一位女参议员，也是第一位在[[美国国会|美国国会]]两院都获得席位的女性。<ref name=umaine>{{cite news|work=University of Maine|title=Senator Margaret Chase Smith (1897-1995)|url=http://mcspolicycenter.umaine.edu/?q=senator-margaret-chase-smith-1897-1995|accessdate=2016-07-09|archive-date=2016-10-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161022054220/https://mcspolicycenter.umaine.edu/?q=senator-margaret-chase-smith-1897-1995|dead-url=yes}}</ref>她是共和党温和派，曾在1950年发表了批评[[麦卡锡主义|麦卡锡主义]]的著名演讲“{{le|良心宣言|Declaration of Conscience}}”。<ref name=speech>{{cite news|work=United States Senate|title=June 1, 1950: A Declaration of Conscience|url=http://www.senate.gov/artandhistory/history/minute/A_Declaration_of_Conscience.htm|accessdate=2016-07-09|archive-date=2016-06-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160607062455/http://www.senate.gov/artandhistory/history/minute/A_Declaration_of_Conscience.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>

史密斯曾参加[[1964年美国总统选举|1964年美国总统选举]]中共和党的总统初选，但未成功。但她也成为第一个在主要政党的大会上提名为[[美国总统|总统]]候选人的女性。<ref name=congress/>2011年1月5日之前，她是历史上任职时间最长的女性参议员，此紀錄後由[[芭芭拉·米庫斯基|芭芭拉·米庫斯基]]打破。<ref name=emkinstitute>{{cite news|work=Edward M. Kennedy Institute for the United States Senate |title=Margaret Chase Smith, Republican of Maine |url=http://emkinstitute.org/updates/entry/featured-senator-margaret-chase-smith |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140309124432/http://emkinstitute.org/updates/entry/featured-senator-margaret-chase-smith |archivedate=2014-03-09 }}</ref>到目前为止，史密斯仍是在参议院任职时间最长的共和党女性。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.nytimes.com/interactive/2013/03/22/us/politics/women-in-the-senate.html?ref=politics|title=Women in the Senate - Interactive Graph|publisher=The New York Times|date=2013-03-21|accessdate=2014-05-14|archive-date=2014-05-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140515005150/http://www.nytimes.com/interactive/2013/03/22/us/politics/women-in-the-senate.html?ref=politics|dead-url=no}}</ref>

